data.description: Just like new! This beautiful craftsman-style home sits on a quarter acre in a quiet cul-de-sac near Camelback East Village. The property features a thoughtful split bedroom floor-plan with vaulted ceilings and 3,180 square feet of living space all on one level. This layout ensures privacy and comfort with a primary suite, guest suite and two additional bedrooms. The primary suite is perfect for the work from home professional with a full attached office with built ins, and a huge en suite bath with a soaking tub, dual vanities, walk-in tile shower and a well appointed walk-in closet. Attention to detail is evident throughout this home with premium features including full audio-video pre-wiring, engineered hardwood flooring, and cherry wood cabinetry. The chefs kitchen includes a full stainless steel appliance package, quartz counter, extra full length cabinetry and don't miss the additional wet bar just off the great room. Heading outside you'll find the fully fenced and fully landscaped back yard space including a pergola covered patio, outdoor cooking area and additional RV or boat parking. This remarkable home is situated just 4 minutes from the Biltmore area with plenty of options for find dining, shopping and entertainment. Call today for your own private tour!
